verses.verse: Jehovah <S%H3068><s%> reigneth <S%H4427><s%>; He is clothed <S%H3847><s%> with majesty <S%H1348><s%>; Jehovah <S%H3068><s%> is clothed <S%H3847><s%> with strength <S%H5797><s%>; he hath girded <S%H247><s%> himself therewith <S%H8398><s%>: The world also is established <S%H3559><s%>, that it cannot be moved <S%H4131><s%>.
Thy throne <S%H3678><s%> is established <S%H3559><s%> of old <S%H227><s%>: Thou art from everlasting <S%H5769><s%>.

Above the voices <S%H6963><s%> of many <S%H7227><s%> waters <S%H4325><s%>, The mighty <S%H117><s%> breakers <S%H4867><s%> of the sea <S%H3220><s%>, Jehovah <S%H3068><s%> on high <S%H4791><s%> is mighty <S%H117><s%>.
Thy testimonies <S%H5713><s%> are very <S%H3966><s%> sure <S%H539><s%>: Holiness <S%H6944><s%> becometh <S%H4998><s%> thy house <S%H1004><s%>, O Jehovah <S%H3068><s%>, for evermore <S%H753><s%>.
